# Cursor Rules for LANEGAP

## Commit Messages

All commit messages MUST be prefixed with an appropriate gitmoji.

Format: `:gitmoji: Concise message in English`

Common gitmojis:
- :lipstick: UI/style changes
- :sparkles: New feature
- :bug: Bug fix
- :recycle: Refactor code
- :fire: Remove code/files
- :wrench: Config changes
- :globe_with_meridians: i18n/translations
- :art: Code structure improvements
- :zap: Performance improvements
- :rocket: Deploy/release
- :memo: Documentation
- :white_check_mark: Tests
- :package: Dependencies
- :truck: Move/rename files

Examples:
- :lipstick: Update button primary styles with gold theme
- :sparkles: Add dynamic champion background on enemy page
- :bug: Fix OTP email sending in production
- :recycle: Refactor header to use Shadcn DropdownMenu

